                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2002" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0308</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9984 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒙牛精选牧场纯牛奶：全流程“可视化溯源”营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mengniu Pure Milk by Selected Pasture: “Visual Traceability” Marketing Process</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李梅，李聪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国传媒大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙道军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒙牛乳业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品安全“痛点”；“可视化溯源”创新营销；搜索引擎传播；2015百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Food safety “pain point”; Visual traceability; Search engine communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了蒙牛作为乳品行业传统企业，深度洞察消费者食品安全“痛点”，结合蒙牛精选牧场纯牛奶产品“奶源”优势，与我国最大互联网公司百度达成战略合作，以互联网创新技术为驱动，打造“云端牧场”概念，推出中国首款“互联网+”牛奶。蒙牛将产品二维码、百度智能硬件设备云摄像头及移动端轻应用三者结合，打破传统产业链时间与地域屏障，实现“可视化溯源”，开创传统企业数字化营销模式。消费者通过观感及声感亲身感知，与品牌进行深度沟通，重塑蒙牛品牌形象，促进销售转化。同时，以百度为传播主平台，PC和移动端资源双屏配合，通过数据驱动精准锁定与全面覆盖兼顾的传播策略初见成效。蒙牛此次创新数字化营销是传统企业与互联网融合的典型案例。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a traditional dairy enterprise, combined with the advantage of mengniu pure milk by selected pasture and in-depth insight of the “pain point” in food safety, MengNiu has reached a strategic cooperation with China’s biggest Internet company Baidu. They have launched the original “Internet+” milk conception, which is the idea of “ranch on cloud”, completed by using the innovative “internet” technology. MengNiu has break though the barriers of timing and geography regards of a traditional industry chain via the technology of product’s two-dimension code combined with Baidu cloud cameras (hardware) and clients’ application (software) on apps, to achieve “visual traceability” for milk resource. It creates a digital marketing mode for traditional enterprises. Consumers are able to communicate with brand more deeply by the sense of visual and sound, which would help MengNiu to recreate its brand and promote selling.  Meanwhile, based on the main communication platform Baidu in both PC and App ends, MengNiu has reached the initial result by its precision lock and universal coverage features via data drive. This innovative digital marketing strategy is actually a showcase of the combination of a traditional enterprise with internet.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新数字化营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-08</td>
                            </tr>
